  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dad\u0dcf \u0d9a\u0dc5\u0ddc\u0dad\u0dca \u0d9a\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "If you do fuel irregularities, tell a number",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Q.R. of the National Fuel License. Electricity and Energy Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera said that photos and pictures of irregularities outside the code can be forwarded to the phone number 0742123123 through UHT.",
        "Filling Stations and staff not operating as per the Energy Minister's terms, illegal fuel collection, fake Q.R. The Minister said that photos, videos and information about individuals or groups printing codes and vehicle registration numbers can be forwarded to the phone and that information will be given to the police for investigations.",
        "Q.R. Minister Kanchana Wijesekera further mentioned that the supply of coded fuel will be suspended."
      ],
